<title>Chamna Lal Apieng Tai</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chamna Lalmang a pieng Bethlehem ah,
 Ziechu gam lailungpen Kanaan gam nuom;
 Namtin dinga kenga tun theihna ahi,
 Ziechun Hinna Lalpa chu a hung pieng hi.

[V2]
 Aw, Lambang pakun, Lalmang Leng pien ni hi,
 Kipakin sai tiu chamna leh nawpna ding;
 Chitin namtin dingin suohchakna ahi'
 Lawpin pak un &quot;Hallelujah&quot; tiu in.

[V3]
 2. Phalbi dap zan khawsawt phuoinel chungah,
 Belam chingte'n a belam ngaknau ah;
 Zankhang laiin Gabri-el a va chiehin
 &quot;Hin le damna thu pha ka hun puoi&quot;a tii.

[V4]
 3. Angel mi thieng sang-za van laizawl ah'
 Hung kilakin chung la go a sau ie;
 &quot;Chungnung pena Pathien lopi pen henla,
 Lei chungah kipah le chamna leng hen&quot; tin.

[V5]
 4. Belampute chun khawpi lam zuonin.
 Khawsak michingte'n le khuo chu zuonin;
 Chibai bukin liengvaite'n a neihsun un,
 Leng leh lal ten a gobawmteu a hawng ui.

[V6]
 5. Kipak hitiu chung le nuoi leng pien ni'n,
 Kingkang leh gi hawih chitin cheng tumin;
 Lal chengte Lal leh pathiente Pathien chu,
 Hinlai damsungin pakbang chawiun Krista.</lyrics>
</song>